Name: Salted Milk Tea
AttributesDescription: Defeating overworld enemies yields 25% more Shell Credits, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A sugary, salty beverage inspired by the favorite tea drink of the miners in Huanglong. During the cold winter months, a bowl of Salted Milk Tea can warm the entire body.
